---
title: Beef Bibimbap Rice Bowl for Dinner with Beef Bulgogi Salad Wraps for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new spin on the recipe to create something
different for lunch the next day. Add classic Asian flavours to beef mince and turn it into beef bibimbap for dinner, then use the
remainder to make beef bulgogi wraps for lunch. Extra delicious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5f03c461fff7c66c36680ffc-3207e90a.jpg
